---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Get in touch with the DealMela team about a deal, a correction, or a partnership."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 pt-10 sm:pt-14 pb-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink mb-6">Contact</h1>
    <div class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed space-y-5 text-[15px] sm:text-base">
      <p>Spotted a price that's changed, found a broken link, or want to suggest a deal? We'd genuinely like to hear it.</p>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-line bg-white/60 p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col gap-4 not-prose">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-ink-faint uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Email</p>
          <a href="mailto:deal.mela26@gmail.com" class="text-brick font-semibold hover:underline">deal.mela26@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-ink-faint uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Response time</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-soft">We typically reply within 2–3 business days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-ink-faint pt-2">
        Note: DealMela doesn't handle order issues, returns, or refunds — those are between you and the retailer (Amazon, Flipkart, etc.) you purchased from.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
